We're looking for a dedicated and inquisitive Data Analyst to help us with data projects. We are looking for a motivated and passionate individual who loves data to join our Customer Insights and Analytics team. Write SQL queries to combine various data assets to extract relevant information

Bachelor’s degree in MIS, Computer Science, or related field; open to entry-level candidates
